    <item>
      <title>欧洲央行决策者认为 10 月降息可能性不大</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/rates-bonds/ecb-policymakers-see-october-cut-unlikely-2024-09-12/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[三位消息人士对路透社表示，欧洲央行决策者认为，除非经济增长前景出现大幅恶化，否则 10 月份降息的可能性不大。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/rates-bonds/ecb-policymakers-see-october-cut-unlikely-2024-09-12/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 12 Sep 2024 16:14:27 GMT</pubDate>
